{"tid":1365471,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"整左個防禦力+1既護手…","createTime":"2019-07-25T15:52:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T15:52:39.000Z","uid":278667,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6e753f513d22d4b09532f0efd88b2c62c27bb0d3","tid":1365471,"uid":278667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:52:39.000Z","msg":"同FD小試牛刀咁整左個護甲<br />\n整得好樣衰請見諒 我張圖有腳睇補番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/25/233103_c4c40f695f16c61268d5602fa29b031c.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F25%2F233103_c4c40f695f16c61268d5602fa29b031c.JPG&h=056434db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n材料十分之簡單<br />\n首先係迪卡儂商城既瑜伽墊 24蚊塊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/11KWizd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F11KWizd.jpg&h=b5223659&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後係中南商城既泡棉 32蚊塊<br />\n順便曬下我個fd隻貓同對腳<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ChaRRUK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FChaRRUK.jpg&h=5e60a7b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後電線膠布 aeon 12蚊商城<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UBNpstA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUBNpstA.jpg&h=59b16de4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後就係呢個魔術貼<br />\n我地買左勁大卷250蚊 中南商城出品<br />\n如果小小地整 50蚊有找既<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/igd4stR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Figd4stR.jpg&h=10602fa7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁點整呢 好很簡單<br />\n首先將瑜伽墊同泡棉剪左做護手size先啦<br />\n咁我就係 瑜伽墊|泡棉|瑜伽墊咁樣疊埋既<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K7RBiBD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK7RBiBD.jpg&h=0f103f22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁瑜伽墊反轉 用cutter輕輕力介幾刀 等佢易屈D<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KHEfzav.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKHEfzav.jpg&h=6c5cbe38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後就剪魔術貼 之後痴上去塊瑜伽墊度(PS：唔好痴落泡棉度 大力D扯會爛)<br />\n記得吉手果一面向出 如果唔係隻手會吉到好痛<br />\n<br />\n之後就用電線膠布將所有野痴埋一齊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MiAqWpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMiAqWpQ.jpg&h=8c1638d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁就完成啦 超級簡單<br />\n熟手左唔洗5分鐘就爆到一件出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n方便大量生產<br />\n<br />\n咁實測過 一拳打落去都係會痛架<br />\n如果想防禦力好D 中間層泡棉要厚D<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後 如果你見到手持武器又無任何辨認既人士<br />\n我建議你都係用盾/走會好D"}]}